{"name": "Grace For Dinner at Grace Presbyterian Church", "alternate_name": "", "description": "A monthly free meal and choice of groceries for anyone in need. Guests pre-order their meal from 2 
options. Orders must be received by the Monday before. 1 meal per person. Any surplus meals are 
handed out 5:45-6 p.m. on a first-come, first-served basis.  
 
Delivery available only to clients with mobility or transportation challenges (must live within 15-mins 
drive of church, approx. 5 miles.). Delivery request must be made when placing order.
